series_title: Insurance Agents or Agency Investigations Life and Health
series_description: This series documents complaints against licensed life and health agents or agencies and the ensuing investigations. series may include, but is not limited to: complaints, investigative reports, medical reports, financial reports and motor vehicle reports, findings, punishments, warning letters and license revocations.

series_title: Insurance Agents or Agency Investigations Property and Casualty
series_description: This series documents complaints against licensed property casualty agents or agencies and the ensuing investigations. This series may include, but is not limited to: complaints, investigative reports, medical reports, financial reports and motor vehicle reports, findings, punishments, warning letters and license revocations.

series_title: Insurance Agents or Agency Investigations Real Estate Settlement Agents
series_description: This series documents complaints against licensed real estate settlement agent (RESA) companies, agents, and agencies. This series may include, but is not limited to: complaints, investigative reports, medical reports, financial reports and motor vehicle reports, findings, punishments, warning letters and license revocations.
